content:
Is dependency support planned to be supported for FSH Online?

Was trying to use it to create an instance of US Core Patient, but it didn't recognize the 'InstanceOf' url.

(Same FSH worked fine with sushi locally, and the dependency set correctly...)

This is something that is definitely in the long term plan for FSHOnline. I've added an issue on the FSHOnline GitHub so that we remember that this is something we should prioritize in the future: https://github.com/FSHSchool/FSHOnline/issues/23. But in the immediate future (next 2 or so weeks), we are focusing on more SUSHI and goFSH related work.
